The **dashboard** links above are charts, not markup — this hub mirrors each
reporting repo's own interactive dashboard so it's viewable even if that
repo has no GitHub Pages of its own. **Daily report** is the plain
`REPORT.md`; open it via this hub's own site to have it render nicely,
since raw GitHub URLs show it as plain text.

